{"tid":2365114,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"約翰遜稱封鎖措施在部分地區見到成效","createTime":"2021-01-13T13:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T13:31:43.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c9c9725001dea36b70ec7d3a62b386ed305f7e39","tid":2365114,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:22:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570246-20210113.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570246-20210113.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=7e3617db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570246-20210113.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=84b9d49b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570246-20210113.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國首相約翰遜表示，政府上星期因應新型肺炎疫情而採取的防疫措施，已經在國內某些地區見到成效，但警告目前仍處於早期階段，亦不排除再實施更嚴格的限制。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜又說，政府將盡快實施每星期七日，每日24小時的疫苗接種計劃，但目前疫苗供應有限。<br />\n<br />\n由於近期住院人數激增，政府計劃將部分患者轉到酒店接受治療。衛生大臣夏國賢說，國民保健署正尋找各種辦法，去減輕醫院的壓力，當局會根據臨床情況作出判斷。<br />\n<br />\n阿斯利康藥廠計劃向英國發放更多疫苗，預計到下月中旬左右，可以每星期提供200萬劑。"},{"pid":"07d7987d2cba56b16643d6cfc9ac5bfce1c55227","tid":2365114,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:30:25.000Z","msg":"每日80000宗減至75000宗"},{"pid":"da9027cfc43be3564aa09e571053bc6d0de82d2a","tid":2365114,"uid":73269,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T13:31:43.000Z","msg":"lort快D去，唔係一好轉，工作同學校都搶唔到"}]}